high_descs: Turn right and walk to the white counter.
Pick up the spray bottle on the left on the counter.
Walk over to the toilet on the other side of the room.
Put the spray bottle down on the back of the toilet.
Turn right and walk back over to the counter.
Pick up the remaining spray bottle on the counter.
Walk back over to face the back of the toilet.
Put the second spray bottle down on the back of the toilet behind the candle.
anns.task_desc: To move two spray bottles to the back of the toilet.

high_descs: Turn right and walk across the room to face the table.
Pick up the spray bottle on the left side of the table.
Turn around and walk across the room to face the back of the toilet.
Place the spray bottle on the back of the sink.
Turn right and walk across the room to face the table.
Pick up the spray bottle on the right side of the table.
Turn around and walk across the room to face the back of the toilet.
Place the spray bottle on the back of the sink next to the other spray bottle.
anns.task_desc: To move two pray bottles from a table to the back of the sink.

high_descs: Turn to your right and go to the counter across from you.
Pick up the yellow spray bottle on the left side of the counter.
Turn around and go to the toilet.
Place the yellow spray bottle on the back of the toilet tank.
Turn to your right and go back to the bathroom counter across from you.
Pick up the yellow spray bottle to the right of the sponge, on the counter.
Turn around and go back to the toilet.
Place the yellow spray bottle on the back of the toilet tank to the right of the candle.
anns.task_desc: Put two spray bottles on the back of the toiklet.
